s have also been seen. When disturbed, see-see partridge prefers to run rather than fly, but if necessary it flies a short distance on rounded wings. The song is a whistled hwit-hwit-hwit. References Pheasants, Partridges and Grouse by Madge and McGowan, ISBN 0-7136-3966-0", "shortSummary": "The see-see partridge (Ammoperdix griseogularis) is a gamebird in the pheasant family Phasianidae of the order Galliformes, gallinaceous bi…", "imageUrl": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6e/See-see_Partridge%2C_Ammoperdix_griseogularis_%285829563744%29.jpg/960px-See-see_Partridge%2C_Ammoperdix_griseogularis_%285829563744%29.jpg?utm_source=en.wikipedia.org&utm_campaign=api&utm_content=thumbnail", "order": "Galliformes", "family": "Phasianidae", "genus": "Ammoperdix", "species": "Ammoperdix griseogularis", "orderCn": "鸡形目", "familyCn": "雉科", "genusCn": "沙鹑属", "speciesCn": "See-see partridge", "kingdomId": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylumId": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "classId": "taxonomy-class-aves", "orderId": "taxonomy-order-galliformes", "familyId": "taxonomy-family-phasianidae", "genusId": "taxonomy-genus-ammoperdix", "speciesId": "taxonomy-species-ammoperdix-griseogularis", "taxonomyIds": {"kingdom": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylum": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "class": "taxonomy-class-aves", "order": "taxonomy-order-galliformes", "family": "taxonomy-family-phasianidae", "genus": "taxonomy-genus-ammoperdix", "species": "taxonomy-species-ammoperdix-griseogularis"}, "expandable": true, "x": -659.29, "y": 640.83, "z": 98.71}, {"id": "taxonomy-genus-ammoperdix", "name": "沙鹑属", "latinName": "Ammoperdix", "type": "taxonomy", "taxonomyLevel": "genus", "summary": "沙鹑属（Ammoperdix）是图谱中的分类级分类节点，当前关联2种鸟类，如See-see partridge、Sand partridge。", "expandable": true, "memberCount": 2, "x": -290.89, "y": -283.18, "z": -54.95}], "links": [{"key": "bird-see-see-partridge-38eecd33__belongs_to_species__taxonomy-species-ammoperdix-griseogularis", "source": "bird-see